\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ulnone While most of the message might address the patient Hippocrates will require the express explicitly who is the receiver of the message.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4 \cf2 say to patient "Message to Patient".\
say to caregiver "Message to Caregiver".\
say to physician "Message to Caregiver".\
\
\
