\f0\b\fs32 \cf2 Dealing with uncertainty\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf2 \
Values that are used in decision might not always be 100% certain. This can have different reasons from aging of value or values that are close to the boundaries of these values. Hippocrates complements every value with a confidence value between 0% and 100%. This can be used to make sure that decisions are based on values that are trustworthy.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf2 \{confidence controlled paragraph\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0 \cf2 \\confidence selector\\ >\
  \{\{\\confidence range selector\\ >\
  \{\{\\paragraph\\ >\
    \\innermost paragraph\\ <\
  \}\}<\}\}\
  [\\other cases\\]\
).\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf2 \
\{confidence selector\}::\
confidence of values
\f4\b0  >> (complete decision)\
0% ... 100%\
\

\f5\b \{confidence range selector\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0 \cf2 \\lower confidence level\\ ... \\upper confidence level\\\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf2 \{lower confidence level\}::\
\{upper confidence level\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0 \cf2 \\percentage100\\\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\i \cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf2 \ul \ulc2 Rules:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ulnone 1. If 
\f0\b \\confidence controlled paragraph\\
\f7\i  
\f1\i0\b0 is used Hippocrates checks each value that is used if it is within the specified confidence range. Once the final decision point, the 
\f0\b \\innermost paragraph\\
\f1\b0  is reached all value that have been used in the decision will be checked again. Only if all of these values are still in that range the 
\f0\b \\innermost paragraph\\
\f1\b0  is executed.\
2. 
\f0\b \\lower confidence level\\
\f1\b0  must be less than 
\f0\b \\upper confidence level\\
\f1\b0 .\
3. If not all possible confidence levels are addressed by using 
\f0\b \\range selector\\
\f1\b0  a 
\f0\b \\other cases\\
\f1\b0  paragraph is necessary.\
4. 
\f0\b \\confidence controlled paragraph\\
\f1\b0  cannot be nested.\
5. Whenever a
\f2\i  
\f0\i0\b \\confidence selector\\ 
\f1\b0 is found Hippocrates will do the following:\
a. Identify values that are used in the current level (no subsequent paragraphs will be evaluated).\
b. Check all values on their confidence level and for those which are below the highest threshold issue a question.\
c. Once the 
\f0\b \\innermost paragraph\\
\f1\b0  is reached re-assess the confidence level of all values that have been used on the path to that 
\f0\b \\innermost paragraph\\
\f1\b0 . If this fails the next lower 
\f0\b \\confidence range selector\\
\f1\b0  will be chosen.\
d. Any 
\f0\b \\value\\ 
\f1\b0 that is changed in the 
\f0\b \\innermost paragraph\\ 
\f1\b0 will have the lowest confidence used on the path to the 
\f0\b \\innermost paragraph\\
\f1\b0 .\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ul \ulc2 \
Example(s):\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ulnone \
Making a decision that changes the dose based on 
\f2\i weight
\f1\i0  and 
\f2\i age
\f1\i0  requires a decent level of confidence in that value.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4 \cf2 ...\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf2 \ul \ulc2 assess
\f4\b0  
\f5\b confidence of values
\f4\b0  >\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ulnone   
\f5\b \ul 80% ... 100% >
\f4\b0 \
\ulnone     assess age >\
      0 years ... 8 year >\
        show message to caregiver "Do not use for children".\
        single dose = 0 tablets. <\
      9 years ... 150 years >\
        assess weight >\
          0.5 kg ... 15 kg >\
            show message to patient "For persons under 15 kg this\
              drug should not be used.".\
            single dose = 0 tablets. <\
          16 kg ... 25 kg >\
            single dose = 2 tablets. <\
          26 kg ... 250 kg >\
            single dose = 3 tablets. <<<\
     <\
  
\f5\b \ul 0% ... 79%
\f4\b0  >\ulnone \
    single dose = 0 tablets.\
    show message to patient "The confidence of the data is not\
      sufficient to calculate a dose. Please ask your physician\
      for your dose." <$\
<\
...\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

