\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 Frequency\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf2 \
Frequency is used to generate repetitive events.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4 \cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf2 \{frequency per time unit\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0 \cf2 \\frequency\\ per \\time unit\\ |\
every \\time unit\\ |\
every \\positive integer number > 1\\ \\time unit\\\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\i \cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf2 \ul \ulc2 Rules:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ulnone 1. If 
\f0\b \\frequency\\ per \\time unit\\
\f1\b0  is used 
\f0\b \\frequency\\ 
\f1\b0 must not be higher as the next smallest 
\f0\b \\time unit\\
\f1\b0 . The means that the maximum frequencies are:\
a. 
\f4 once per second\

\f1 b. 
\f4 60 times per minute
\f1 \
c. 
\f4 60 times per hour\

\f1 d. 
\f4 24 times per day\

\f1 e. 
\f4 7 times per week
\f1 \
f. 
\f4 31 times per month\

\f1 g. 
\f4 366 times per year\

\f1 For months and years the numbers will be corrected according to actual length of the month in the respective year or according to leap years.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf10 \strike \strikec10 Documentation\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf10 \strikec10 \
Hippocrates does not allow comments as all elements of the script should have an actual meaning. However, there is a possibility to add comments at any position in the script. As one core concept of Hippocrates is local language support that language context of comment must be provided.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f6\i\b \cf10 \strikec10 \{documentation\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0 \cf10 \strikec10 documentation (\
  \{\{<language> (\
    <text>\
  ).\}\}\
).\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf10 \strikec10 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf10 \ul \ulc10 \strikec10 Examples:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf10 \ulnone \strikec10 \
A comment can be inserted at any position in a Hippocrates script. Ideally the comment is so meaningful that it could also be shown to the \'84outside\'93 world.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\i \cf10 \strikec10 "Riamet 20/120mg tablets" is a drug (\
  documentation (\
    english (\
      Here a documentation of the drug should go.\
    ).\
    german (\
      Hier sollte die Beschreibung des Medikamentes stehen.\
    ).\
  ).\
  valid units (\
    asses unit (\
      tablet (unit is valid.).\
    ).\
  ).\
  \
  dosage safety (\
    maximum single dose = 4 tablets.\
    minimum time between single doses = 8 hours.\
  ).\
\
  single dose calculation (\
    assess pregnancy (\
      pregnant (\
        single dose = 0.\
      ).\
      not pregnant (\
        assess weight (\
           0.5 kg ...   4.9 kg (single dose = 0 tablets.).\
           5.0 kg ...  14.9 kg (single dose = 1 tablet.)\
          15.0 kg ...  24.9 kg (single dose = 2 tablets.)\
          25.0 kg ...  34.9 kg (single dose = 3 tablets.)\
          35.0 kg ... 250.0 kg (single dose = 4 tablets.)\
        ).\
      ).\
    ).\
  ).\
\
  administration schedule (\
    first dose trigger is "first dose administrated".\
     8 hours after first dose administration.\
    24 hours after first dose administration.\
    36 hours after first dose administration.\
    48 hours after first dose administration.\
    60 hours after first dose administration.\
  ).\
).\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
