\f0\i0\fs32 \cf2 Intended use\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf2 \
Hippocrates requires the definition of the intended use of a script. This provides the possibility to request signing of these scripts by registered persons. This is mainly intended to help the recipient \
of a script to make a decision on use.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf2 \{intended use\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0 \cf2 intended use >\
  \\intended use description\\\
  \{\{\\intended use options\\\}\}\
).\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\i \cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f6\b \cf2 \{intended use description\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0 \cf2 short description is \\text\\.\
[long description is \\text\\.]\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f6\b \cf2 \{intended use options\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0 \cf2 intended use is medical.\
intended use is non-medical.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strike \strikec2 intended use is clinical trial.\
intended use is diagnosis.\
intended use is treatment.\
intended use is follow-up.\
intended use is behavioral change.\
intended use is ...\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strike0\striked0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\i0\b\fs32 \cf2 Sharing\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf2 \
In addition to sending information using 
\f0\b send message
\f1\b0  Hippocrates provides means to send the actual raw data to any 
\f0\b \\addressee\\
\f1\b0 . In any case Hippocrates request consent to share the data. This consent either be given for all values that are requested on a per 
\f0\b \\addressee\\
\f1\b0  basis.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf2 \{sharing chapter\}::\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0 \cf2 sharing. >\
  share with \\addressee\\|\\addressee group\\\
    \{\{; \\addressee\\|\\addressee group\\\}\} >\
    \\event\\ >\
      \{\{\\share paragraph\\\}\} <<\
<\
\
