\cf2 \ul \ulc2 Examples:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ulnone \
The following example shares all data that is available for a patient with an addressee (which could be a clinical data manager or even platforms like PatientsLikeMe). The sharing will only be possible, if the patient or caregiver has given the consent to share these information. This needs to be set using the Hippocrates UI. For that purpose Hippocrates will screen all values that are supposed to share and will ask fro consent to share these values. The values themselves will be packaged in JSON-format.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf2 \ul \ulc2 sharing >\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0 \cf2 \ulnone   
\f5\b \ul share with clinical data manager >
\f4\b0 \ulnone \
    every Friday at 8:00 pm >\
      context >\
        timeframe is between (7 days ago ... now)! <\
      
\f5\b \ul share all values of all plans >
\f4\b0 \ulnone \
        after delivery failure >\
          show message to patient "The weekly data summery\
            could not sent to the clinical data manager.\
            We will get in contact with you shortly to\
            assess the problem.".\
          send message to service provider\
            "We do not get data from trial participant XYZ.\
            Please get in touch with that person within next\
            2 hours.". >\
              after delivery failure. >\
                show message to patient "We cannot automatically\
                  inform our service provider to assess the data\
                  upload problem. Please call XXX-XXX-XXXXX.". <\
              after delivery success. >\
                show message to patient "We contacted our service\
                  provider. If you do not receive a call within\
                  next 2 hours, please call XXX-XXX-XXXXX.". <<<<<<\
<\
