      "Yes" > 
\f5\b \cf7 first dose has been administrated
\f4\b0 \cf2 . <\
      "No"  > repeat question. <<\
  <\
  after 
\f5\b \cf15 first dose has been administrated
\f4\b0 \cf2  >\
    ...\
  ).\
).\
