\
  valid units >\
    assess unit >\
      kg; lb > unit is valid. <<<\
\
  valid values >\
    criteria >\
      value is between (0.5 kg ... 150.0 kg)?\
      
\f5\b \ul source of value is device?\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ulnone       \ul name of device for value is "Withings scale"?\ulnone  <\
